prcStep.stepDesc: MassGIS downloaded the polygon data from https://malegislature.gov/Redistricting/NewDistricts/House and projected the data to Mass. State Plane NAD 1983 Mainland Meters. MassGIS then incorporated a coastline into the dataset using 2020 TIGER/Line "faces" data downloaded from the U.S. Census Bureau.
